= PostGIS Install Guide =
The following is a guideline to install PostGIS onto various operating systems from either prebuilt packages (where maintained) or source.

See the [wiki:UsersWikiPostgreSQLPostGIS PostGIS/PostgreSQL and other dependency matrix] that defines recommended versions of core dependencies for each version of PostGIS.

